Registration is now open for your favourite conference - the International Statistical Ecology Conference (ISEC2020) - to be held on June 22-26, 2020 in Sydney Australia.



Abstract submission is due by December 2 2019.  Bursaries are available to presenters from developing countries.



Plenary speakers:

- Christl Donnelly (Imperial College, London)

- David Borchers (St Andrews)

- Di Cook (Monash)

- Kiona Ogle (Northern Arizona)

- Mark Bravington (CSIRO)



Invited sessions on:

- Reproducible Science

- Methods for high throughput community data



